there is an ancient hindi saying ‡§Ü‡§¶‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§™‡•á‡§π‡§ö‡§æ‡§® ‡§â‡§∏‡§ï‡•á ‡§ú‡•Ç‡§§‡•ã‡§Ç ‡§∏‡•á ‡§π‡•ã‡§§‡•Ä ‡§π‡•à a dude is known or judged by the kind of shoes heshe wears footwear is one of the least significant aspect of our lives hence the idea that you judge a person by how much attention and care they give to that least aspect although rooted in oldschool cynicism and most of us progressives may not agree with it at all it is still followed in most public facing industries like restaurants financial sector manufacturing etc you wear the wrong kind of footwear in these places and see how youe judged

coming back to the product these bata sandals no doubt 100 live up to the care and attention paradigm not only are they reasonably priced and attractive looking i think their usp is the surface comfort you get which is missing in most sandals these days it has only been a couple of days since i\m using these but having used similar bata branded sandals earlier i can confidently say that this is long lasting material

just ensure that the size is correct by looking at the size measuring chart before ordering it might save you lot\s of hassles happy shopping sandal should be light in weight jut good to wear the gap between the leather straps pinch my skin when it bends it was uncomfortable and im wearing socks to spare myself the pain that was overlooked in the design otherwise the quality is good and it is comfortable  with socks the sandal fits well and it is true to its size the quality is also quite good considering the standard wear and tear it will be an excellent choice for occassional wear with traditional dresses the pricing on amazon though is a bit disappointing as it dropped by 100 from the purchase price within a week i thought 630 was a decent price point only to find out that it can be had for half of that price recommend the product since few months functioning as usual its really excellent look n comfortable good value for money
